'''''Da Yie''''' (izwi kandi ku izina ry'icyongereza '''''Good Night''''' ) ni filime ngufi yasohotse  muri 2019 iyobowe na Anthony Nti<ref>Incredible Ghanaian film posters - BBC Culture <nowiki>https://www.bbc.com</nowiki> › culture › article › 20190313-inc...</ref> <ref>Ghanaian film 'Da Yie' reminds us to hold onto that innocence <nowiki>https://www.theafricareport.com</nowiki> › ghanaian-film-da-yie...</ref>. Muri 2020, yatsindiye iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Clermont-Ferrand  kandi yari mu bahatanira ibihembo bya BAFTA Los Angeles Awards<ref>Ghana provides inspiration for Anthony Nti's award-winning ... <nowiki>https://www.baystatebanner.com</nowiki> › 2021/03/25 › ghana-...</ref>. ''Filime Da Yie'' yakozwe na Anthony Nti, Chingiz Karibekov na Dimitri Verbeek, ikwirakwizwa ku isi yose na sosiyete mpuzamahanga yo gutunganya no gukwirakwiza filimi Salaud Morisset<ref>MY TAKE: Why Anthony Nti’s award-winning film ‘Da Yie’ is more than a movie (ewn.co.za)</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Umusore Matilda na Prince bajyanwa murugendo ruhindura ubuzima numuntu utazwi<ref>DA YIE (GOOD NIGHT) - FILM AFRICA 2020 <nowiki>https://www.filmafrica.org</nowiki> › film-africa-2020 › da-yie</ref>.<ref>Ghanaian Rapper-Turned-Director Taps Traditional Themes ... <nowiki>https://www.voanews.com</nowiki> › ghana-film-taps-traditional...</ref>.

== Ibihembo ==
Kuva yatangizwa, iyi filime yatoranijwe mu minsi mikuru irenga 130 ku isi. Muri Gashyantare 2021<ref>Ghana's anti-corruption blockbuster film draws crowds - BBC</ref>, yakoze urutonde rwibikorwa bya firime ngufi ya Live ibihembo bya 93 bya Academy<ref>Anthony Nti's Award Winning Film DA YIE shares a story of ... <nowiki>https://www.jbklutse.com</nowiki> › oscar-film-by-ghanaian-dire...</ref> . 
